commit.message: Run CI with Pillow too

Add support for transparent backgrounds

Fixes #64
Update changelog for v0.12.0
Add forward-compatibility with Pillow 8.0.0
Drop redundant code

Use pre-commit to keep things tidy

- Use black. Formatting is a mess.
- Use mypy. Though more love is required here, especially since we have
  inconsistent APIs. This should help pick up on them.
- Configure flake8 in a compatible way.
- Reorder imports.
Add with_doctype to the changelog
